574
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:08,020
It's okay.

575
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,060
Xiaoling is back.

576
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:12,780
It's none of my business.

577
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:16,460
You were a couple before.

578
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:18,220
Even though it's over,

579
00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:19,300
you're still friends, right?

580
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,540
Jiali,

581
00:25:21,140 --> 00:25:22,940
