Why should you decide everything?

585
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:41,140
Weren't you the ones who abandoned him?

586
00:25:41,380 --> 00:25:42,260
Speak properly.

587
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:46,220
No matter how unpleasant we were
in the past,

588
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:47,700
we should respect

589
