600
00:26:13,020 --> 00:26:13,860
Go inside.

601
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:14,970
Stop talking.

602
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:16,500
Why go inside?

603
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:18,900
