604
00:26:19,700 --> 00:26:21,220
Let's go home!

605
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:24,380
Are you crazy?

606
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:27,500
Ignore him.

607
00:26:27,940 --> 00:26:28,780
Sit and talk.

608
00:26:31,300 --> 00:26:32,140
Zhenmin,

609
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:33,780
have a good talk with Jiali.

610
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:39,580
Zhenmin.

611
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:40,540
No way.

612
00:26:41,460 --> 00:26:43,500
Xiaoling hasn't neglected Yangyang.

613
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:45,660
Once her financial situation was better,

614
00:26:45,900 --> 00:26:47,700
