615
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:48,820
Jiali,

616
00:26:48,980 --> 00:26:50,060
it's not about the money.

617
00:26:53,540 --> 00:26:54,700
I understand you.

618
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:56,500
