But over these years,

624
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:07,700
she's faced storms alone outside.

625
00:27:08,940 --> 00:27:11,940
We can imagine her hardships.

626
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:13,460
But she was far away,

627
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:14,700
no one could help her,

628
00:27:14,700 --> 00:27:15,700
take care of her.

629
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:17,940
She had to rely on herself.

630
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:21,500
Sometimes she even had no money
to buy food,

631
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:23,700
