632
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:24,620
She deserved it.

633
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:32,660
It wasn't easy for her
to come back this time.

634
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:34,700
She just wants to see the child.

635
00:27:35,700 --> 00:27:37,620
She doesn't have any other intentions.

636
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:38,980
She told me that

637
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:40,940
