to the child in the future.

638
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:44,220
Zhenmin,

639
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:46,140
just see this as an act of kindness.

640
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:50,700
No woman wouldn't care for her child.

641
