Yangyang,

645
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:27,500
come with me. Let's go home.

646
00:28:28,380 --> 00:28:29,700
Your Mom is back.

647
00:28:30,700 --> 00:28:31,700
Don't you miss your Mom?

648
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:32,780
