679
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:15,140
I'm not crying.

680
00:30:15,460 --> 00:30:16,460
I'm not.

681
00:30:16,460 --> 00:30:18,300
Things are getting better.

682
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,260
It won't be tougher than before.

683
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:23,060
When the baby is born,

684
00:30:23,260 --> 00:30:24,700
call me,

685
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:26,700
and let us know.

686
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:28,900
Of course.

687
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:30,740
Get in the car.

688
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:34,700
I'll rent out your house.

689
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:36,220
The rent will be transferred
to your account.

690
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:37,740
