695
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:46,300
Yes, it's safe.

696
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:49,380
Xiaoling is a priority now.

697
00:30:49,460 --> 00:30:50,540
I'll take care of her.

698
00:30:50,540 --> 00:30:51,380
Alright.

699
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:52,900
Take care of yourself.

700
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:54,980
Xiaoling,

701
00:30:55,780 --> 00:30:57,700
be cautious out there.

702
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:00,500
Mr. Huang,

703
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:02,860
