when you can.

704
00:31:02,940 --> 00:31:03,780
Sure.

705
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:04,900
Huang,

706
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:07,700
since our family isn't nearby,

707
00:31:08,660 --> 00:31:10,460
