711
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:17,980
Don't worry.

712
00:31:23,900 --> 00:31:27,020
Xiaoling, let me know when the baby is born.

713
00:31:27,020 --> 00:31:28,220
I'll come to visit you.

714
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:29,740
