- Xiaoling.

736
00:32:40,220 --> 00:32:41,180
I'm leaving, Jiali.

737
00:32:47,060 --> 00:32:48,060
Alright, go ahead.

738
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,300
Take care of yourself.

739
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,380
