860
00:39:27,620 --> 00:39:28,660
Your Grandma is still here.

861
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:31,420
Jiali will take care of her.

862
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:32,660
The two of them

863
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:34,580
live here for such a long time

864
00:39:34,940 --> 00:39:35,820
and don't pay rent,

865
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:37,030
shouldn't they contribute something?

866
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:41,140
Jiaxi, you are here.

867
00:39:41,140 --> 00:39:42,660
Jiali, you're back.

868
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:45,740
Mom, I am leaving now.

869
00:39:45,740 --> 00:39:46,660
The shop needs to open.

870
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:49,260
Have some watermelon before you go.

871
00:39:49,260 --> 00:39:50,180
No, thanks, Jiali.

872
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:01,580
I want to ask you something.

873
00:40:01,980 --> 00:40:02,980
What's that?

874
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:06,620
How's Xiaoling's house?

875
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:07,980
It's almost settled.

876
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:10,580
What are your plans for it?

877
00:40:11,580 --> 00:40:12,420
Rent it out.

878
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:16,460
I'll rent it.

879
00:40:18,660 --> 00:40:19,540
Why?

880
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:22,780
Well, I was thinking...

881
00:40:23,180 --> 00:40:24,660
I've been staying here all the time,

882
00:40:24,980 --> 00:40:27,380
I need a change of scenery.

883
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:30,660
Was it Jiaxi's idea?

884
00:40:33,580 --> 00:40:34,420
Honestly speaking,

885
00:40:34,420 --> 00:40:37,460
I planned to take Jiaxi in.

886
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:38,980
Are you taking her in,

887
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:40,180
or is she taking you in?

888
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:42,580
Or she wants to use your name,

889
00:40:43,340 --> 00:40:44,540
and stay in Xiaoling's house?

890
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:49,540
I said it's rented. I'll pay the rent.

891
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:53,500
Xiaoling's rent

892
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:56,580
