893
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:58,380
It's a subsidy for Yangyang.

894
00:40:58,420 --> 00:40:59,580
No disputes allowed.

895
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:01,180
If Jiaxi lives there,

896
00:41:01,420 --> 00:41:02,980
