897
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:04,820
Of course you should.

898
00:41:05,140 --> 00:41:06,980
But what if she can't pay one day?

899
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:08,140
Can I kick her out?

900
00:41:16,540 --> 00:41:17,460
Jiali,

901
00:41:18,500 --> 00:41:19,860
Jiaxi

902
00:41:19,860 --> 00:41:22,180
is really struggling right now.

903
00:41:22,460 --> 00:41:23,660
Her store

904
00:41:23,660 --> 00:41:27,300
