and she still needs to pay rent.

905
00:41:27,580 --> 00:41:29,380
Xiaoling's house is bigger.

906
00:41:29,420 --> 00:41:30,460
If she pays rent,

907
00:41:30,580 --> 00:41:33,020
she'll have to pay more.

908
00:41:35,420 --> 00:41:37,540
Alright, you talk to Jiaxi later.

909
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,820
No problem. I'll talk to her.

910
00:41:39,620 --> 00:41:43,020
Mom, please stay out of this.

911
00:41:43,460 --> 00:41:45,140
Xiaoling is already struggling enough.

912
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:46,740
