923
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:14,180
Grandma said she couldn't chew meat.

924
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:15,860
It gets stuck and is hard to digest.

925
00:42:17,380 --> 00:42:18,580
Would you like some Pork Floss?

926
