Jiaxi, it's a call for you.

931
00:42:38,180 --> 00:42:39,020
Who is it?

932
00:42:39,060 --> 00:42:39,900
Jiali.

933
00:42:40,060 --> 00:42:40,900
Jiaxi,

934
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:42,060
