935
00:42:42,060 --> 00:42:44,860
Xiaoling's house was rented yesterday.

936
00:42:44,860 --> 00:42:45,980
The contract was already signed.

937
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:48,940
No worries, Jiali.

938
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:50,340
I was just asking casually.

939
00:42:50,660 --> 00:42:51,500
No worries.

940
00:42:52,340 --> 00:42:53,580
Let's meet and chat sometime.

941
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:55,060
It's late. You should sleep now.

942
